item.title: CVE-2024-29116|2024-03-19T14:54:16.891Z -- IconicWP -- WooThumbs for WooCommerce by Iconic
item.description: Improper Neutralization of Input During Web Page Generation ('Cross-site Scripting') vulnerability in IconicWP WooThumbs for WooCommerce by Iconic allows Reflected XSS.This issue affects WooThumbs for WooCommerce by Iconic: from n/a through 5.5.3.
